{"tid":1671511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【討論】放棄民陣 成立『武當』","createTime":"2019-10-23T13:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T08:53:59.000Z","uid":288154,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7e6b21e4aa1b7f65fb9c6fcc4d04c72a41980376","tid":1671511,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:48:57.000Z","msg":"剛過去的遊行，大家明知係義士以武制暴，一樣有數十萬民眾支持，直掃多條大路。即係話&hellip;勇武功勞已得到大家認同。<br />\n<br />\n係時候比對家更大壓力喇！提升勇武在運動中江湖地位，正式宣告，成立『武當』，以另一個名字發起集會遊行，講到明會『以武制暴 裝修中舖』。當然沒有大台，你我他各巴絲都可以在連登TG發起，通告各大中小媒體，並且也可以申請不反對通書。<br />\n<br />\n而民陣方面，武當勇者配合一下，日後民陣的集會遊行，只數人數不動武。<br />\n<br />\n留給大家討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"d5cd15989f90a1c6d32da38fa1861b9a90c6104b","tid":1671511,"uid":60977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:51:46.000Z","msg":"figo講野唔錯<br />\n公關幾好<br />\n<br />\n民陣連續兩個發言人都係LSD既人<br />\n耐人尋味"},{"pid":"bac8d51ddb5fb75c4a99e29a9d1ccdcd51da9338","tid":1671511,"uid":205785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:56:04.000Z","msg":"公開號召人做犯法嘢，同送頭有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6740acc40362e36f7bb20f5b6d05a24401cdab","tid":1671511,"uid":322508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:56:51.000Z","msg":"點解無人推行動..<br />\n<br />\n最新 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">主線</span></span></strong> 日程表  (未能收納全部，請見諒。)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MWU0S5O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMWU0S5O.png&h=e01304d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUavpbD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUavpbD.jpg&h=5efe45aa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nu5LjKK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnu5LjKK.jpg&h=0b0ebc02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\